data.description: This wonderful custom-built home is on an elevated lot in the heart of the Monarch Golf Course * A brand new roof will be installed before closing. This home is close to the restaurant, pro shop and Great Hall for convenience. The HVAC system was replaced in 2009 and the home has double-pane windows and pocket doors. The front door with side light welcomes you into a tiled foyer, then to the formal living room. The spacious kitchen has a gas range, a closet pantry and an inviting breakfast nook that's the perfect place for enjoying your morning coffee. The split floor plan provides added privacy and comfort. The home also has volume ceilings and there are sliders leading to a huge Florida room, perfect for entertaining. There is a huge master suite with a generous walk-in closet. The Master bath boasts dual sinks, another sizable walk-in closet, a luxurious garden tub and a separate shower. The guest suite has two generously sized bedrooms and guest bath with a shower. One of the bedrooms can be used as an office or den. The 2-car oversized garage gives you ample space for you vehicles and much more. The pull-down attic stairs provide easy access to additional storage.  There is also a window for lots of natural light and a side-entry service door for easy access. Royal Highlands is a premier resident - owned gated community.18 hole golf course, restaurant and pro shop. 2 pools (one indoor one outdoor). Lit tennis courts, pickleball, shuffleboard bocci ball courts. Softball field, billiards, fitness, card rooms and library. Great Hall for social functions, fitness classes, concerts, plays etc. HOA also includes cable and internet plus secure RV/ Boat parking and storage.
